<!DOCTYPE html>
<html dir="ltr" lang="en-GB">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
		<link href="css/style.css" rel="stylesheet" media="all" />
		<link href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Source+Sans+Pro:400,400italic,700,300" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="none" onload="if(media!='all')media='all'">
		<title>My ESA Assessment</title>
		<!--[if lt IE 9]>
			<script src="js/html5.js"></script>
		<![endif]-->
	</head>
	<body>
		<header role="banner">
			<span role="image" aria-label="SEAP assessments ESA logo">My ESA Assessment</span>
			<nav role="navigation" class="to-main-menu">
				<ul>
					<li>
						<a href="javascript:void(0)" data-action="menu">Main Menu</a> 
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="javascript:void(0)" data-action="stats">My Assessment</a>
					</li>
					<li>
						<a href="javascript:void(0)" data-action="data">My Data</a>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</nav>
		</header>
		{{#each questions}}
		<div class="slide question" id="question-{{sluggify question}}" data-category="{{sluggify category}}">
			<div class="question-container">
				<!--<img src="path/to/question-icon.svg" alt="" />-->
				<h2 class="question-text" tabindex="-1">
					<span class="activity">Activity: {{category}}</span>
					<span class="vh">Question:</span>
					<em>{{question}}</em>
				</h2>
				<div class="answers" aria-label="choose an answer">
					{{#each answers}}
					<label>
			            <input type="radio" value="{{value}}" name="{{sluggify ../category}}"> <span>{{label}}</span>
			        </label>
					{{/each}}
				</div>
				<ul aria-label="menu">
					<li>
						<button data-followup="#{{followUp}}" class="nav-link pick" data-action="pick">Ask me another</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link stats" data-action="stats">My assessment so far</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link break" data-action="break">I need a break</button>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		{{/each}}
		{{#each advice}}
		<div class="slide advice" id="{{sluggify title}}">
			<div class="flow">
				<!--<img src="path/to/advice-icon.svg" alt="" />-->
				<h2 class="advice" tabindex="-1">
					{{title}}
				</h2>
				<p class="description">{{description}}</p>
				<div class="things-to-remember">
					<h3>Things to remember</h3>
					<p>Check any items you want added to <strong>Your Reminders</strong> checklist, which you can print out with <a data-action="stats" href="javascript:void(0)">your other assessment info</a>.</p>
					<ul>
						{{#each tips}}
						<li>
							<label>
								<input type="checkbox" value="save" data-tip-id="{{sluggify this}}"> <span>{{this}}</span>
							</label>
						</li>
						{{/each}}
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		{{/each}}
		<div class="slide qualify" id="qualify-high">
			<div class="box green">
				<h1 tabindex="-1">
					You may qualify for<br/>
					<strong>Support Group</strong>
				</h1>
				<p>Your answer to the last question shows that you may qualify for the highest ESA allowance, placing you in the &#x201c;Support Group&#x201d;. Do you want to try more questions?</p>
				<ul aria-label="menu">
					<li>	
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="pick">Another question</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="stats">My assessment so far</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="menu">Main menu</button>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="slide qualify" id="qualify-low">
			<div class="box green">
				<h1 tabindex="-1">
					You may qualify for<br/>
					<strong>Work Related Activity Group</strong>
				</h1>
				<p>Your answer to the last question shows that you may qualify for the standard ESA allowance, placing you in the &#x201c;Work Related Activity Group&#x201d;. It&#x2019;s still possible that you may qualify for a higher rate. To find out, try some more questions.</p>
				<ul aria-label="menu">
					<li>	
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="pick">Another question</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="stats">My assessment so far</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button href="#main-menu" class="nav-link">Main menu</button>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="slide break-time" id="break-time">
			<div class="box">
				<img src="images/tea.png" alt="steaming cup of tea" />
				<h1 tabindex="-1">You&#x2019;re on a break</h1>
				<p>Feel free to close the window or turn off your computer and come back when you&#x2019;re ready. Everything will be as you left it :-)</p>
				<ul aria-label="menu">
					<li>	
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="resume">Continue</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="menu">Main menu</button>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="slide deleted" id="deleted">
			<div class="box">
				<h1 tabindex="-1" style="red">Deleted</h1>
				<p>All of your assessment data has been successfully deleted from your computer.</p>
				<ul aria-label="menu">
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="menu">Main menu</button>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="slide get-started" id="start">
			<div class="box">
				<h1 tabindex="-1">Let&#x2019;s begin</h1>
				<p>In your real assessment you&#x2019;ll be asked questions about your ability to do activities. Here, you can try out some of these questions and be told how you might do in a real assessment. You can <a role="button" href="#break-time" data-action="break">take a break</a> at any time and come back later. Your computer will remember where you were in the app :-)</p>
				<div><button class="nav-link" data-action="categories">Choose an activity</button></div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="slide get-started" id="seen-all">
			<div class="box green">
				<h1 tabindex="-1">No more new questions</h1>
				<p>You&#x2019;ve seen all the questions (so you&#x2019;re pretty familiar with the assessment now!) but you skipped some. What would you like to do?</p>
				<ul aria-label="menu">
					<li>	
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="skipped">Skipped questions</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="stats">My assessment so far</button>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="slide get-started" id="seen-all-even-skipped">
			<div class="box green">
				<h1 tabindex="-1">Practise Complete!</h1>
				<p>You&#x2019;ve answered all the practice questions available, so you&#x2019;re pretty well versed now. What would you like to do next?</p>
				<ul aria-label="menu">
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="stats">How did my assessment go?</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="restart">Practise again</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="menu">Main Menu</button>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="slide get-started" id="resume">
			<div class="box">
				<h1 tabindex="-1">Hello again?</h1>
				<p>Looks like you&#x2019;ve been here before. Press &#x201c;continue&#x201d; if you want to go back to where you were. Not been here before? Choose &#x201c;main menu&#x201d;.</p>
				<ul aria-label="menu">
					<li>	
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="resume">Continue</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="clean-up">Main menu</button>
					</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="slide stats" id="stats">
			<div class="stats-container">
				<div id="stats-content" class="flow"></div>
			</div>
		</div>
