			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="slide main-menu" id="main-menu">
			<div class="flow">
				<h1 tabindex="-1">My ESA Assessment</h1>
				<p class="larger">Welcome to our <abbr title="Employment And Support Allowance">ESA</abbr> website, designed to help you get ready for your ESA assessment. This website is <strong class="tick">run independently and impartially</strong> by the charity SEAP, <strong class="tick">does not collect your personal data</strong> and contains <strong class="tick">no long, boring forms!</strong></p>
				<div role="toolbar" aria-label="menu options">
					<ul>
						<li class="half">
							<button data-action="about-esa">All about ESA <span>and your assessment</span></button>
						</li>
						<li>
							<button data-action="start-or-resume"><i aria-hidden="true">&#x2605;</i> Practise <i aria-hidden="true">&#x2605;</i> <span>by assessing yourself</span></button>
						</li>
						<li>
							<button data-action="stats">My Assessment <span>and how it&#x2019;s going so far</span></button>
						</li>
						<!--<li class="half">
							<button data-action="answering-questions">Answering <span>questions the right way</span></button>
						</li>
						<li class="half">
							<button data-action="prep" data-prep-slug="travel">Travelling <span>to your assessment</span></button>
						</li>-->
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
		<div class="slide category-finished" id="category-finished">
			<div class="box">
				<h1 tabindex="-1">Well done!</h1>
				<p>You&#x2019;ve seen all the practise questions about <strong id="this-activity">this activity</strong>. What would you like to look at next?</p>
				<ul aria-label="menu">
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="categories">A new activity</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="stats">My assessment so far</button>
					</li>
					<li>
						<button class="nav-link" data-action="menu">Main menu</button>
