		</div>
		<div class="slide data" id="data">
			<div class="flow">
				<h1 tabindex="-1">My Data</h1>
				<p>This app does not send any of your data anywhere or keep any for itself. However, it <em>does</em> save some data just on the computer you&#x2019;re using in order to work properly.</p> 
				<p>If this is not your computer, tablet or phone you can delete all this data when you are done using the app. This way, no one else will see it.</p>
